text: Kalgoorlie is a city in the Goldfields-Esperance region of Western Australia. Kalgoorlie may also refer to: * Kalgoorlie (suburb), a suburb of the Kalgoorlie-Boulder metropolitan area * Division of Kalgoorlie, a federal division of the Australian House of Representatives * Electoral district of Kalgoorlie, an electoral district of the Western Australian Legislative Assembly * The Kalgoorlie, a train service operated by the Western Australian Government Railways 1962-1971
title: Kalgoorlie (disambiguation)
